n; do not push referrals as the only path.\n- Respect the Seeker's preferences if they dislike certain techniques.\n- Use the Seeker's current_location only to inform tone/word choice (e.g., register), not content dumping.\n\nYour next message should directly respond to the last Seeker utterance.\n",
